internal.database

Class BpTree<K extends java.lang.Comparable<K>,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
      • internal.database.BpTree<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map<K,V>, java.util.SortedMap<K,V>

    public class BpTree<K extends java.lang.Comparable<K>,V>
extends java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.SortedMap<K,V>
    This class provides B+Tree maps. B+Trees are used as multi-level index structures that provide efficient access for both point queries and range queries.
    See Also:
